"Tuhan ada di dalam dirimu."

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:26.120
"Kamu menerangi dunia."

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:30.240
"Mengapa hidupmu penuh dengan kesedihan?"

00:04:31.760 --> 00:04:35.440
"Bhagya Lakshmi."

00:04:39.240 --> 00:04:42.160
"Bhagya Lakshmi."

00:04:46.640 --> 00:04:49.360
"Bhagya Lakshmi."

